	Judge Lopez    
	 London, Sept. 15 (PTI): Pop star and actress Jennifer Lopez has reportedly agreed to a $12 million deal to be an American Idol judge instead of her initial demand of $15 million.      
	Lopez held talks with Idol producers over joining the panel of judges after the departures of Simon Cowell, Ellen DeGeneres and Kara DioGuardi.      
	It was reported that Lopez had intitially asked for $15 million to be a judge on the show plus a guaranteed motion picture deal and a number of TV programmes.       
	However, her demands were refused.
                                                                                                                                                      
